[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
Zhamel installs its EFI binary at:

  ${PREFIX}/share/efi/FreeBSD/zhamel.efi

Typical deployment on FreeBSD:

  install -m 0644 ${PREFIX}/share/efi/FreeBSD/zhamel.efi \
      /boot/efi/EFI/FreeBSD/loader.efi

For encrypted-root boot you will also need the matching zhamel_zfskey kernel
module package once it is added to this ports tree.
EOM
}
]
